TextBody:
Hi Naeemah,
 
Thank you for your time today.
 In today's meeting, we reviewed your SQL jobs and acknowledged that the running time had increased after the upgrade.
We noticed the number of threats assigned to the job (4 threats), and we suspected that could be one reason why it was taking longer to run. We agreed to increase it to 8 to see if that made any difference. I will review the log to see if there is anything related to the increase in the time.
You can reply to this email to provide an update. Let me know if increasing the number of threats makes a difference.
 
Thanks,

Hi Naeemah,

Thank you for your time today.
 In today's meeting, we reviewed your SQL jobs and acknowledged that the running time had increased after the upgrade.
We noticed the number of threats assigned to the job (4 threats), and we suspected that could be one reason why it was taking longer to run. We agreed to increase it to 8 to see if that made any difference. I will review the log to see if there is anything related to the increase in the time.
You can reply to this email to provide an update. Let me know if increasing the number of threats makes a difference.

Thanks,
